videos.description: Kodi Justice picks up the steal and slam for the Sun Devils.
videos.headline: Justice slams it home after the steal

videos.description: Tra Holder fights for the loose ball and finishes the layup after taking contact.
videos.headline: Holder finishes acrobatic layup after steal

videos.description: Dallas Walton slams it with ease after a great no-look pass from McKinley Wright.
videos.headline: Wright drops no-look dime to Walton for slam

videos.description: Shannon Evans shows off his hang time going up-and-under for Arizona State.
videos.headline: Evans goes up-and-under on the baseline

videos.description: De'Quon Lake makes it look too easy on the posterizing dunk for the Sun Devils.
videos.headline: Lake puts defender on a poster

videos.description: George King buries the outside jumper as Colorado and Arizona State continue to go back and forth.
videos.headline: King's three puts Colorado ahead

videos.description: Romello White gets the tough bucket underneath to go as the fans go crazy in Tempe.
videos.headline: White battles for the tough and-1

videos.description: Arizona State's Shannon Evans knocks down the corner three after Tra Holder comes up with the block and assist.
videos.headline: Evans buries a triple off a great play from Holder
